## IMPORTANT
- Use React useState for expanded steps (toggle on click)
- Poll with useEffect + setInterval when run is not terminal
- Handle empty/loading states gracefully
- Export as named export
- Format durations as seconds (e.g., '2.1s')
- Parse JSON output when possible, fall back to raw text
